                    <content>
                      <p>
                        <ref href="/akn/il/act/PrimaryLegislation/1961-04-06/147844">בחוק מס רכוש וקרן פיצויים, התשכ"א–1961</ref> – <ref href="/akn/il/act/PrimaryLegislation/1961-04-06/147844#point_36א">סעיף 36א(ב)</ref>;</p>
